## How to Run

### Step 1 вЂ” Create MySQL Database
```sql
CREATE DATABASE fastapi_crud;
```

### Step 2 вЂ” Update [.env](file:///c:/Users/gishi/coding/fastapi-crud/backend/.env)
```
# backend/.env
DB_URL=mysql+pymysql://root:YOUR_PASSWORD@localhost:3306/fastapi_crud
```

### Step 3 вЂ” Start Backend
```bash
cd backend
pip install -r requirements.txt
uvicorn main:app --reload
```
> The [items](file:///c:/Users/gishi/coding/fastapi-crud/backend/routers/items.py#9-12) table is **created automatically** on first run.

### Step 4 вЂ” Start Frontend
```bash
cd frontend
npm run dev
```
Open **http://localhost:5173**

