## How it Works (Code Tour)

| File | Role | Key Concept |
|------|------|-------------|
| [database.py](file:///c:/Users/gishi/coding/fastapi-crud/backend/database.py) | DB connection | `SessionLocal`, [get_db](file:///c:/Users/gishi/coding/fastapi-crud/backend/database.py#16-22) dependency |
| [models.py](file:///c:/Users/gishi/coding/fastapi-crud/backend/models.py) | DB schema | SQLAlchemy `Column` definitions |
| [schemas.py](file:///c:/Users/gishi/coding/fastapi-crud/backend/schemas.py) | Validation | Pydantic `BaseModel` |
| [crud.py](file:///c:/Users/gishi/coding/fastapi-crud/backend/crud.py) | Business logic | Plain Python functions using Session |
| [routers/items.py](file:///c:/Users/gishi/coding/fastapi-crud/backend/routers/items.py) | HTTP layer | `@router.get/post/put/delete` |
| [main.py](file:///c:/Users/gishi/coding/fastapi-crud/backend/main.py) | App entry | Wires everything together |
| [App.jsx](file:///c:/Users/gishi/coding/fastapi-crud/frontend/src/App.jsx) | React state | `useState` + `useEffect` for CRUD |
| [api/items.js](file:///c:/Users/gishi/coding/fastapi-crud/frontend/src/api/items.js) | HTTP client | Axios calls to the API |

